<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
We are investigating increased error rates and latency in creating new IAM roles in the US-EAST-1 Region and we continue working towards resolution. Previously created roles are not impacted.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 7:19 AM and 8:20 AM PDT, we experienced elevated error rates and latencies creating or accessing IAM entities and authenticating against newly created entities. AWS Services that make use of new IAM users and roles may have been affected. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
